OL,3,CCampaigner seeks High Court claim
OL,4,Cagainst the Gambling Commission
OL,6,FAnnie has argued that the Commission's
OL,7,Frefusal to act represents an
OL,8,Funacceptable failure to fulfil its
OL,9,Fregulatory duties and raises serious
OL,10,Fconcerns about its ability to protect
OL,11,Fpeople from gambling-related harm.
OL,13,FShe is seeking the permission of the
OL,14,FHigh Court to challenge the
OL,15,FCommission's decision by judicial
OL,16,Freview.
